data.title: Looting Black Lives Matter GIF by Salim_Adam

user.description:
Salim Adam is a 3D photographer from London, England.

His work was first recognised on the main stage when he shot 3D gifs for the popular music video 'Mura Masa - What if I go', which received a Vimeo Staff Pick.

Salim has since made his name through his striking gifs online - personalising  his own 'flashing gif'. He is also heavily influenced from his Graphic Design background.

Salim has worked with a number of  brands such as Nike, Adidas, New Balance and Puma.
He has also worked with a range of musicians including, Stefflon Don, Stormzy, Mura Masa, IAMDDB and Octavian.

Email:
info@salimadam.com
